    <briefdescription>
<para>TLS key generation class implemented according to C++ singleton design pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The <ref refid="class_key_gen" kindref="compound">KeyGen</ref> class use the <ulink url="https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls">mbedtls crypto library</ulink>. See details in <ulink url="https://mbed-tls.readthedocs.io/projects/api/en/development/">Mbed TLS API documentation</ulink> It provide a init method which generate the TLS key pair if not exisiting, <linebreak/>
 a method to check if keys are generated, a method to check if public key is transfered to backend, methods to retrieve public and private key, methods to priont out a key, a method to set the indicator that public key is transfered and a methos to delete all key related files. This last function is only for development purposes. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
